Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Lup?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă e adevărat, atunci nu există nicio îndoială cu privire la această amenințare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Dacă nu vreți ca partenera voastră să fie dusă la biserică,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,stați cuminți până ne terminăm afacerea."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar nu avem nicio garanție că nu o vor duce acolo după.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și noi am investit puternic deja în monedele Trenni de argint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă ne vom retrage, pierderile noastre vor fi imense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noi trebuie să lovim primii!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's assume we rescue your partner and take her into asylum here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they report us and the Church searches this building,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'll have no choice but to be as obedient sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can't hide as long as she's in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can leave town together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be caught unless you're extremely lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that happens, you might be taken to a different town and face persecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There would be nothing we could do in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can pay them off,\Nconsidering how much potential profit is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only we had a card to play against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My company could take the initiative and tell the Church that Medio Trading has your companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we do, you'll have a problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might even give damaging testimony against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main point of the scheme
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is to receive special rights from the king of Trenni, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potrivit rapoartelor noastre,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,familia regală are mari probleme financiare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's evident from the fact that they're planning to melt the currency in circulation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and decrease its silver content to issue a larger volume of coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If ten coins become thirteen, that's a profit of three coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll instantly raise funds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the country's reputation will fall under scrutiny and hurt them in the long term.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the Trenni Royal Family to do this anyway proves that they're in financial trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, depending on how the negotiation goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,mining rights, minting rights, tariff rights, and market administration rights are just a sample
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of what the Royal Family may grant for our coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's exactly as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before Medio presses charges,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,finish negotiating with the Royal Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and use the rights as a bargaining chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure her value is insignificant compared to those privileges.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we should sell the rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they believe that they'd be better off buying your rights than crushing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medio Trading will gladly pay the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They have a trump card that could send us to the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last thing the Trenni royals want is trouble with the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't want the public to know that they dealt with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a trading company that was sent to the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we incur the wrath of the Church, they'll eventually turn\Nagainst the king, who'll be held responsible by association.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way Medio Trading will prosecute,\Nsince that would bring about the ire of the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they'd still be reluctant to just back off without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the only thing they could do is bring us down with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's where we offer the privileges in exchange for money and your companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In theory your plan makes perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's a significant obstacle to its implementation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as I can guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medio Trading has yet to collect many silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they had a significant amount of coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they would have headed to the Church the moment they captured Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That they chose to forego that option and approach us here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is proof of their lack of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This plan is one that endeavors to exploit a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medio will have had to keep their coin-gathering quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}, what do you propose to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We retrieve Holo and I flee with her until you've finalized a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm unable to escape, I can buy you some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Collect as many coins as you can and begin the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, do you plan to tell the Church about Holo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to face my testimony if it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With your help, I'll be able to evade capture for at least a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, my partner in crime is a wolf spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If her only goal is escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she uses her true abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no human will be able to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long will you need to assemble enough coins to command the king's attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I dispatch someone by horse right now, he should reach Trenni Castle by dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the negotiations occur immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'll return by dawn tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now? You don't even know how many coins you'll be able to collect, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guesswork has its place in negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine as long as we secure the coins by the time they're due.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you reach a quick settlement with a king?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any deal can be finalized promptly if we put our minds to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, do you know where Holo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are Milone Trading, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ambush of our employees and arson of our facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are facts of daily life for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have contingencies for any emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We do have one rival, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it the Church?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They visit more towns and countries than we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they're surprisingly well-prepared for crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should the Church launch a search in earnest, you must not run without thinking. Stay hidden in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I would have liked to have known who\Nwas backing Medio Trading before we started negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we would know where their funds were coming from\Nand might even be able to convince them to fund us instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's not ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pray for your safety and success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your hopes will be met in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The passwords are Pireon and Numai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two great gold coins, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed auspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I'm underground, I should touch the right-hand wall and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you hit a wall, you've reached your destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holo will be inside the storage room above.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your retrieval of the hostage will occur as soon as the bell signals that the market is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If everything goes smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the hatch above the path will open and your partner will descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should you hear the word "Rahhe,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,please wait for an escort to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you hear Perouso, make your escape together along the planned route at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rahhe and Perouso.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosperity and famine, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simple to remember, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect them to be so prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard tell of the Church digging graves as a pretense
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to construct underground routes for spying on heretics and evading taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow me. We're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope they don't have to resort to blades or clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I trembling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rahhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rahhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pireon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to carry this so people will think we're thieves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't come down if you're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you staring at? This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold this and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pireon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you made it safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Life in business is full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our guide is down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll remove the ladder and exit another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll then leave town once he informs his contacts about Medio's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're rather prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved you're unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're relieved to see I'm unharmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holo... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holo, the wise wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can remember every single person who ever shamed me in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must add a new name to that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to come and save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I was so convinced that {\i1}you{\i0} came, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel angry just thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a male, aren't you? Shouldn't you have been at the forefront, fighting tooth and nail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you hid in a hole in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You let me make a fool of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't die as long as you hold on to the wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Human males are easy prey since I'm so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, not one of my opponents were fit to be my mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They turned pale in fear as soon as I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll sever your private parts if you so much as touch me."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when {\i1}she{\i0} appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you guess who was among those who captured me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl from Pasloei Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She apparently heard my name from Zheren.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you speak with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were simply a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A wolf spirit lives within the village's wheat fields and determines the quality of the harvest on a whim."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many years it's been since I settled down in that land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe as many as there are hairs on my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Holo, the wise wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to provide the greatest harvest, I let the soil rest on occasion by producing a poor yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was all part of managing the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wheat would have grown better there than anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that the people of the village worshipped me as their god of harvest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but not out of respect. It was more akin to a desire to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who reaps the last stalk of wheat is locked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what Chloe said to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she heard my name from Zheren, and it made her wonder if I was {\i1}her{\i0} Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was happy, as shameful as that sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, she didn't stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gone are the days of having to court your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to gnash our teeth at your fickle nature anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll send you to the Church and bid farewell to all those dated traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, look at it a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to leave the wheatfields in order to return to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they say you won't be missed, blind them with the dust cloud you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be a cleaner break that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be leaving quietly, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, I mean we, are merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We profit, we triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll laugh when we make money,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and cry when we don't have a cent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I think we'll end up laughing.{oh, my release is good actually}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a proper conversation in hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My emotions are far too fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the second time I've cried in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I would have done so even had {\i1}you{\i0} not been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only brought you along to help me make money, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our job is to run for as long as we can until Milone Trading negotiates a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having someone crying and carrying on in the middle of that is just a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So regardless of who was crying in front of me, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm. A female's privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you run out of things to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man behind Medio Trading is Count Ehrendott.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The merchant within the Count's manor in charge of\Nbrokering wheat is responsible for collecting the silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Report this to Marlheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Consider it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true, then, that those who bring talk of profit are rather odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, you mean my ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking at you two makes me want to live the life of a traveling merchant again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I advise against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll end up stuck with someone like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with that. The seat of a wagon is too big for one person anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely I'm the unfortunate one,\Nto be picked up by the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too clever by half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what makes me so charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that much is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are an adorable boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamne.
